text: "Run Baby Run" is a 2005 song by alternative rock band Garbage. It was taken from their fourth studio album Bleed Like Me. It was released as a single in Australia and Europe and went to number 47 in Australia and number 97 in Germany. ==Track listing== *Australia CD maxi single *European CD maxi single # "Run Baby Run" – 3:58 # "Honeybee" – 4:02 # "Never Be Free" – 4:28 # "Badass (October 2003 Ruff Demo)" – 3:15 ==References== Category:Alternative rock songs Category:2005 songs Category:Garbage (band) songs
